  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaor2_yanbaoPPT_3745_2",
    "text": "Worldwide, 31 percent more consumers said they're eating healthier food, continuing a trend we've observed over the past two years. However, the latest survey results also show that consumers today aren't necessarily equating healthy eating with buying products that are labeled \"natural\" or \"organic.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10319767451160608,
      0.40451745368648573,
      0.2718023290971104,
      0.5092402460667612
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_yanbaoPPT_3745",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaor2_yanbaoPPT_3745_35",
    "text": "1 Respondents: 7,000 millennials (ages 20-34), 2,500 Gen X (35-50), 2,000 baby boomers (51-69) 2 Fiqures may not sum to 100%. because of roundina",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5755814084829399,
      0.4640657086458033,
      0.7848837245305825,
      0.47650771381358364
    ],
